version_description:
Hello Helvaulters!
On this update we bring you new features and huge performance improvements!

- Bring cards to your collection via CSV import!
- Huge performance improvements when handling larger collections

If you love the app please let us know by rating us on the AppStore!

For feature requests or any other help, please reach us out on Twitter @helvault_mtg
